r-bit.description: This bit (the `Router' bit) indicates whether the originator is an active router.

dc-bit.description: This bit describes the router's handling of demand circuits.

process.description: Clear an OSPFv3 process based on the process-id.
Clear an OSPFv3 process based on the process-id.
